l | title = APO-PRIMIDONE | accessdate = 2007-01-10 | date = 2007-01-10 | publisher = Apotex }}</ref> '''Liskantin''' (Germany, '''Desitin)''',<ref name=destinin.de>{{cite web | url = http://www.desitin.de/index.php/article/detail/766 | title =  Liskantin | accessdate = 2005-07-03 | publisher = Desitin}}</ref> '''Resimatil''' (Germany, [[Sanofi-Synthélabo]] [[GmbH]]),<ref name=netdoktor.de>{{cite web | url = http://www.dkv.com/content_appl.phtml?content=http://dkv.netdoktor.de/redesign/medikamente/100001437.htm | title = Resimatil Tabletten | accessdate = 2005-07-03 | publisher = Deutsche Krankenversicherung AG }}</ref> '''Mylepsinum''' (Germany, [[AWD.pharma]] [[GmbH]] & Co., [[Kommanditgesellschaft|KG]]).,<ref name=dvk.netdoktor.de>{{cite web | url = http://www.dkv.com/content_appl.phtml?content=http://dkv.netdoktor.de/redesign/medikamente/100001217.htm | title = Mylepsinum Tabletten | accessdate = 2005-07-03 | publisher = Deutsche Krankenversicherung AG }}</ref> and '''Sertan''' (Hungary, 250&nbsp;mg  tablets, [[ICN Pharmaceuticals Inc.]][http://www.kfki.hu/chemonet/mkl/mkl98/mkl10/icn.html])

